snippet.title: Guild Boss | Official Trailer | Watcher of Realms
snippet.description:
Tap to watch the trailer for battles against the Guild Boss! Download Watcher of Realms NOW! Tons of rare items are waiting for you:  https://app.adjust.com/s8bh0dy_kdu6ngu?campaign=cg&adgroup=cg&redirect_macos=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fapp%2Fid1585948508

Ready for the most nerve-wracking game mode -- Guild Boss in Watcher of Realms? From the depths of its mighty belly, the dragon unleashed a torrent of scorching flames, threatening the very existence of the Land of Tya and all who call it home. Take up your sword, brave Commander, and lead your heroes into the ultimate test of courage and skill. The fate of all hangs in the balance as you charge forward to face the most perilous battle of your lives. Together with your Guild buddies is the only way out. Divide and conquer the dragon to reap rich rewards!
Hush now! We've hidden an easter egg in the video! Will your keen eyes be able to find the hidden CD-Key? 

*NOTE: The deadline to redeem the CD-Key is 12/31/2023. Hurry and find the CD-Key to claim your prizes before time runs out~ Tick tock!
